<p>Microsoft offers students a lot of software for free - except for Microsoft Office. This includes various Windows opperating systems. If you are currently in a CIT class, go <a href="https://msdn02.e-academy.com/elms/Security/Login.aspx?campus=byuidaho_is" target="_self">here</a> and enter your BYUI email address and password. If that doesn't work, use their "I've forgotten my password" function. If you then need additional help, please contact the department secretary at <a href="mailto:staigera@byui.edu">staigera@byui.edu</a> or &nbsp;208-496-3621 or in SMI 231.</p>
